    "Failed to sync with App Store. Please check your network connection." : {

    },
    "Feature" : {

    },
    "Follow these steps to enable notifications:\n\n1. Tap 'Go to Settings' button\n2. Find '%@' app in Settings\n3. Select 'Notifications' menu\n4. Turn on 'Allow Notifications'\n\n💡 Recommended settings:\n• Show on Lock Screen\n• Show in Notification Center\n• Show as Banners\n\nThis ensures you never miss timer alerts!" : {

    },
    "Follow these steps to enable notifications:\n\n1. Tap 'Go to Settings' button\n2. Find 'Rereminder' app in Settings\n3. Select 'Notifications' menu\n4. Turn on 'Allow Notifications'\n\n💡 Recommended settings:\n• Show on Lock Screen\n• Show in Notification Center\n• Show as Banners\n\nThis ensures you never miss timer alerts!" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "以下の手順で通知権限を有効にしてください：\n\n1. 「設定へ移動」ボタンをタップ\n2. 設定アプリで「Rereminder」を探す\n3. 「通知」メニューを選択\n4. 「通知を許可」をオンにする\n\n💡 推奨設定：\n• ロック画面に表示\n• 通知センターに表示\n• バナーとして表示\n\nこれでタイマーアラートを見逃しません！"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "아래 단계를 따라 알림 권한을 켜주세요:\n\n1. '설정으로 이동' 버튼을 누르세요\n2. 설정 앱에서 '두번알림' 앱을 찾아주세요\n3. '알림(Notifications)' 메뉴를 선택하세요\n4. '알림 허용(Allow Notifications)'을 켜주세요\n\n💡 권장 설정:\n• 잠금 화면에 표시\n• 알림 센터에 표시\n• 배너로 표시\n\n이렇게 하면 타이머 알림을 놓치지 않고 받을 수 있습니다!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
